name: Higher States of Being  - Vol 2 #001
prompt: stylish astronaut wearing a space helmet and a [clothing], facing half right. Rendered in a cyberpunk brush style with slightly reduced color fidelity, showcasing more muted neon colors and softer dynamic strokes, yet maintaining the futuristic and gritty aesthetic. The soft fabric contrasts with the sleek, reflective surface of the helmet, set against a dark background that subtly enhances the colors and stylistic shading, creating a moody and atmospheric effect.
